Directory: src/styles
Purpose: Centralized styling files and CSS layout definitions.
Responsibility: Houses modular Vanilla CSS styles for widgets, widgets layouts, map controls, and dark/glassmorphism design systems.
Key Files:
- variables.css: Semantic theme colors (hsl based), border radii, blur parameters, and sizing tokens.
- layout.css: Grid and Flex layouts for sidebars, map containers, and absolute UI overlays.
- components.css: Card, input, button, slider, and custom popup styles.
